{"tid":2458661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩台大戰】李克勤加盟任《聲夢傳奇》導師　ViuTV組20位KOL女團硬撼TVB","createTime":"2021-03-23T14:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T00:44:16.000Z","uid":212249,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6468302eb9d58f8faeab8ac48e12960ae1754e07","tid":2458661,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2910000/2913883/tvb_thumb_20210323_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2910000%2F2913883%2Ftvb_thumb_20210323_S_600.jpg&h=afedd48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由余詠珊及何哲圖負責的大型選秀節目《聲夢傳奇》，在曾志偉回巢後曾緊急煞停，而TVB與三大唱片跟無綫「破冰」將《聲夢傳奇》重新包裝推出，更有李克勤擔任《聲夢傳奇》導師。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，ViuTV力邀20位本地KOL打造特備單元劇節目《YOLO的練習曲》，相信能掀起電視界的龍爭虎鬥。<br />\n<br />\n李克勤加盟《聲夢傳奇》<br />\n<br />\n據悉在王祖藍的提議後，《聲夢傳奇》獲重新包裝放行，日有有指重量級歌手李克勤將任星級導師，指導《聲夢》15位學員，同時有指再有三大唱片派出歌手客串《聲夢傳奇》，當中不乏重量級歌手。<br />\n<br />\n李克勤回應傳媒時表示會全力以赴，為學員提供意見，自己也會在節目展示嚴厲的一面。<br />\n<br />\n以「要還原香港音樂」為目標的曾志偉，上任後積極與各部門聯繫，更與香港三大唱片公司接頭，解決了自2009年發生的「版權風波」，修好了TVB與三大唱片公司僵持多年的關係。<br />\n<br />\n今次《聲夢傳奇》重新包裝再推出，15位實力唱將加上專業歌手，豐富節目的追看度。<br />\n<br />\nViuTV本地KOL組女團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2910000/2913883/yolo_20210323_1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2910000%2F2913883%2Fyolo_20210323_1_600.jpg&h=2b956139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於擅長真人騷節目的ViuTV，日前則宣布邀請20位香港KOL和YouTuber女神上陣，打造特備單元劇節目《YOLO的練習曲》，以女團角度深入女性話題。<br />\n<br />\n從宣傳片可見，20位女生以校服Look練舞，當中有「港版周子瑜」之稱的Jeannie、「試當真」常規演員陳苡臻（Jessica）、Dear Jane《未開始已經結束》MV女主角歸南茜（Nancy）、YouTuber戴月（Kikko）、演員郭爾君（Alma）、張蔓姿（Gigi）等。"},{"pid":"e91f06085efbdd7731572f802b67e313bbba180a","tid":2458661,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2913883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2913883&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97bM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e2502418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2913883</a>"},{"pid":"b9e8fb5a00e77b337454ef338d89e21744abbaf4","tid":2458661,"uid":325556,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"笑死 把自己看得那麼高"},{"pid":"d71e8c126f38ab9d1962b7474a5c8175da62b5d6","tid":2458661,"uid":135280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"送禮勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd2dc0bbe4cbba32f2e7fe82816b5f9c1e02b40","tid":2458661,"uid":2419,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"送禮勤咪又係得d老野會睇 冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0931e531545a434b7304398906372b23a0448be5","tid":2458661,"uid":10504,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"你都ON9 <br />\n睇女好過睇CD機屌人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1088a1e7ba43d3fd9b50b6d148758dd920647f77","tid":2458661,"uid":224533,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"殘酷一丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273e27e1f6c55d8eaf405d7e20cf8723337995cc","tid":2458661,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1088a1e7ba43d3fd9b50b6d148758dd920647f77","tid":2458661,"uid":224533,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"殘酷一丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b25da8fea7f695c7f79a8991cec2a27fe0eab08","tid":2458661,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0